QuestData.Title: Fruitful Ventures
QuestData.Description: Oh no! They must be vegetarians.$B$BWhat these elekk need is fruit and lots of it. There are cherries all over the place around here under the trees.$B$BYou wouldn't mind grabbing me some, would ya?
QuestData.CompletionText: I heard the worst rumor about how you have to obtain those things.$B$BSomething about talbuk first eating them and then 'processing' them, and then... well, I don't want to talk about it.
QuestData.RewardText: You got them all? I just know this is going to work.
